[p 
	[a class=extlink href=http://www.filespace.org/PunchRockgroin/WallDeath.fcm rel=nofollow 
		"http://www.filespace.org/PunchRockgroin/WallDeath.fcm
	]a
	" - How to jump through a wall and kill yourself without left+right, pretty self-explanatory.  Truncated, sorry your idea couldn't make it into the movie, but it's here now at least!
	$LF
]p
[p 
	[a class=extlink href=http://www.filespace.org/PunchRockgroin/Invincibility.fcm rel=nofollow 
		"http://www.filespace.org/PunchRockgroin/Invincibility.fcm
	]a
	" - If you slash on the last possible frame before a projectile hits you, it may pass through you instead.  The projectile has to be at a certain position relative to you, though, which is why I never got to use it in the run.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	[a class=extlink href=http://www.filespace.org/PunchRockgroin/4-2AltRoute.fcm rel=nofollow 
